  | title =Simaroubaceae
  | work =Flora of Taiwan, Volume 3, 2nd Edition
  | publisher =
  | date =1993
  | url =http://tai2.ntu.edu.tw/udth/bin/fot1.exe/browse?bid=3&page=545
  | format =
  | doi =
  | accessdate =2007-05-29  }}</ref> It is listed as endangered in the [[IUCN Red List]] of threatened species due to loss of habitat for building and industrial plantations. <ref>{{cite web
  | last =Pan
  | first =F.J.
  | authorlink =
  | coauthors =
  | title =Ailanthus altissima var. tanakai
  | work =2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species
  | publisher =
  | date =1998
  | url =http://www.iucnredlist.org/search/details.php/31349/all
